{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"requestProgress","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requestProgress","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"meth